# Paper Pipeline — PUBLIC repo .gitignore
# 此版本：EXCLUDE projects/*（除了 _template/）、EXCLUDE PDFs；只追蹤工具本身

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/
env/

# --- Env / Secrets ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.key

# --- IDE / OS ---
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Research projects: 只保留 _template，不公開任何具體研究 ---
projects/*
!projects/_template/
!projects/.gitkeep

# --- PDFs（無論如何不公開） ---
*.pdf

# --- Runtime artifacts ---
logs/
*.log
projects/*/search_papers*.py
